      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Petra X is enjoying a road trip across the NE USA" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Petra X is enjoying a road trip across the NE USA" href="/user/show/1237196-petra-x-is-enjoying-a-road-trip-across-the-ne-usa">Petra X is enjoying a road trip across the NE USA</a>
