      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3633533-cutting-for-stone">Quotes from Cutting for Stone</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
